00:39:49.760 --> 00:39:50.880
(tomes en serio)

00:39:50.880 --> 00:39:51.670
(este examen,)

00:39:52.590 --> 00:39:53.630
(pero siendo honesto,)

00:39:54.800 --> 00:39:56.110
(aprender desde cero)

00:39:56.360 --> 00:39:57.880
(no vas a aprobar en un mes,)

00:39:58.760 --> 00:39:59.840
(pero si puedes aprender algo)

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.030
(de este examen,)

00:40:01.550 --> 00:40:02.710
